  description: "At the start of battle, increases Lifesteal Rate by 15%. When receiving
    a fatal blow, Thanatos does not die. Instead, He seize the attacker\u2019s soul
    and form a pact with the demon. During that turn, all incoming damage is redirected
    to that enemy. At the start of the next turn, restores 25% of Max HP and increases
    Lifesteal Rate by 15% for 2 turns."
